{"meta":{"title":"Phoebe's blog","subtitle":"分享一些学习上的心得经验","description":"高露在Github上的个人博客","author":"Phoebe Gao","url":"http://oppalu.github.io"},"pages":[{"title":"Categories","date":"2016-12-15T06:25:25.000Z","updated":"2016-12-06T21:21:38.000Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"http://oppalu.github.io/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"Tags","date":"2016-12-15T06:25:25.000Z","updated":"2016-12-06T21:21:38.000Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"http://oppalu.github.io/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: org.apache.jsp.index_jsp问题的解决","slug":"java-lang-ClassNotFoundException-org-apache-jsp-index-jsp问题的解决","date":"2016-12-15T06:37:25.000Z","updated":"2016-12-15T06:44:12.000Z","comments":true,"path":"2016/12/15/java-lang-ClassNotFoundException-org-apache-jsp-index-jsp问题的解决/","link":"","permalink":"http://oppalu.github.io/2016/12/15/java-lang-ClassNotFoundException-org-apache-jsp-index-jsp问题的解决/","excerpt":"","text":"在学习JSP与JavaBean的过程中，自己写了一小段代码，代码结构如图 此时使用运行时发现出现了500异常，异常情况如图 在网上查阅资料均说这种异常出现是因为jar包与Tomcat自身的jar包冲突，而我本身使用Tomcat服务器，并没有引入外部jar包。后来查看控制台，发现有下列的warning提示 我想会不会是class路径有问题，后来试着将原本在src下的JavaBean文件放入了自定义的包中，结果运行正常。查阅资料并没有发现需要这样做的根本原因，只看到了说JavaBean的开发要求有：①所有的类必须放在一个包中，在Web中没有包的类是不存在的②所有类必须声明为public class③属性用private封装，提供getter、setter方法④一个JavaBean中至少存在一个无参构造方法","categories":[{"name":"J2EE","slug":"J2EE","permalink":"http://oppalu.github.io/categories/J2EE/"}],"tags":[{"name":"J2EE","slug":"J2EE","permalink":"http://oppalu.github.io/tags/J2EE/"},{"name":"JSP","slug":"JSP","permalink":"http://oppalu.github.io/tags/JSP/"},{"name":"JavaBean","slug":"JavaBean","permalink":"http://oppalu.github.io/tags/JavaBean/"}]}]}